Design a premium floating AI Counsellor assistant UI.

Design Philosophy:
Quiet, confident, non-intrusive.
Feels like a senior counsellor presence.

Idle State:
- Circular avatar (44â€“48px)
- Neutral background
- Subtle border
- Fixed bottom-right
- No animation

Attention State:
- Soft pulse or halo
- No text labels
- Only when action is required

Expanded State:
- Compact card panel
- Max width ~300px
- Show:
  1) One guidance sentence
  2) Max two action buttons
- No scrolling
- No chat history

Voice Controls:
- Voice Assistant button only in expanded state
- Dictation mic stays inside text input

Rules:
- Never auto-open
- Never steal focus
- Never block UI
- Respect PRD stage rules

Constraints:
- No flashy gradients
- No new colors
- No heavy animations

Goal:
A premium AI presence that feels calm, trustworthy, and intelligent.
